Project Outline
  - General
    - Kaijo minimap
    - Display logo on wall
    - Differentiate avatar color based on roles
    - User-Agent ways of interaction 
      - video
      - voice
      - chat
  - Company
    - Movable avatar, can go to interested booth 
    - customizable booth (based on package)
    - Present
    - Q&A
    - receive application (resume)
    - on-spot interview
  - Job Hunter 
    - Movable avatar, can go to interested booth 
    - Listen to presentation
    - Q&A
    - Apply for position
    - on-spot interview

